item.title: Picture This: A Photo Essay | Enlight Blog
item.description:
Picture This: A Photo Essay | Enlight Blog

With your iPhone in hand, you are a storyteller. Your photos are your words. You are no longer taking pictures, you're creating them. A Picture is Worth a Thousand Words You have certainly heard of this time-honored adage which states that a complicated idea can be conveyed with just a single image.
